<p>This week is a special week because you get TWO Mac Geek Gab episodes instead of just one (and then they&rsquo;re off next week). Dave and John come back to help solve Mail.app date confusion, keyboard &amp; trackpad freezes, contact syncing problems, and a big discussion about what to &mdash; and what not to &mdash; delete from your Mac. Additionally, they have a comment from an Apple Genius about just what happens &mdash; and how it all works &mdash; when you get your Mac repaired at the Genius Bar. Don&rsquo;t miss this one, folks!</p>
